        "ggHboygj04d_text": "<p><span style=\"color:#000000;\">You’re not imagining it.</span> Something <i>is</i> quietly draining your focus, drive, and prosperity signal every single night. <span style=\"color:#000000;\">Egyptian</span> historians called it the <span style=\"color:#000000;\">“Law of Diminishing Light.”</span> And according to <span style=\"color:#000000;\">Amara Callen’s</span> recent research, this ancient warning wasn’t metaphorical, it was <span style=\"color:#000000;\"><i>scientific</i>.</span> Because when your <span style=\"color:#000000;\">frequency weakens after 35</span>, so does your luck. But for the first time in centuries, the code to restore it <span style=\"color:#000000;\"><strong>has been decoded.</strong></span></p>",
